---
interface Props {
  topicsCount: number;
  resourcesCount: number;
  postsCount: number;
}
const { topicsCount, resourcesCount, postsCount } = Astro.props;
---
<section class="pb-8">
  <div class="container-shell grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr_0.9fr]">
    <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-fuchsia-400/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-500/20 to-violet-500/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-fuchsia-100">Core pillars</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold text-white">{topicsCount}</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200">Each pillar now acts like a guided learning track instead of a static content block.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-cyan-400/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/20 to-sky-500/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-100">Resource kits</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold text-white">{resourcesCount}+</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200">Downloadable guides, notes, and modules are surfaced through interactive filters.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-amber-400/20 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-400/20 to-orange-500/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-amber-100">Fresh insights</p>
      <p class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold text-white">{postsCount}</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-200">A new blog stream keeps the site alive with reflections, updates, and thought leadership.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
